## Privacy Notice

This application:
- Processes SMS messages locally on device
- Uses Google Gemini API for classification (requires internet)
- Sends notifications via Telegram (optional)
- Does not collect analytics or telemetry
- Does not share data with third parties (except Gemini API for classification)
- Stores all data locally on device

Users are responsible for:
- Securing their API keys
- Complying with local privacy laws
- Understanding data processing implications

